00:03:41,613 --> 00:03:48,936
So the first question that a lot of people ask when they hear about charter review is what is a city charter?

42
00:03:50,256 --> 00:03:54,558
It's often referred to as the constitution of a city.

43
00:03:55,118 --> 00:04:04,882
It creates the city of Medford as a legal entity, it establishes the city's powers, and it outlines the broad fundamentals of the city government.

44
00:04:05,722 --> 00:04:07,303
So it's a very important document.

45
00:04:09,265 --> 00:04:10,926
So why review?

46
00:04:11,226 --> 00:04:13,328
This is another question that people ask.

47
00:04:13,828 --> 00:04:15,469
Well, there's a lot of reasons.

48
00:04:15,649 --> 00:04:19,571
One is to keep up with the modern understanding of best practices.

49
00:04:20,912 --> 00:04:23,973
Medford's charter hasn't been reviewed in decades.

50
00:04:25,454 --> 00:04:27,615
It was reviewed in the 1970s.

51
00:04:27,675 --> 00:04:30,797
It was changed, the last change was in the 1980s.

52
00:04:31,437 --> 00:04:35,300
So it's been a long time since it's been looked at and a lot has changed since then.

53
00:04:36,721 --> 00:04:44,610
Another reason is to respond to the needs and preferences of residents and maintain consistency with state and federal law.

54
00:04:45,851 --> 00:04:52,840
Because of the nature of our charter, it works in conjunction with state law and it hasn't been looked at in a long time.

55
00:04:55,401 --> 00:05:05,103
There could be conflicts with state law and updating it, looking at it periodically helps maintain consistency with state and federal law.

56
00:05:05,983 --> 00:05:10,064
Also remaining consistent with community values and cultural changes.

57
00:05:10,964 --> 00:05:15,565
Our city has changed a lot in the decades since the charter was last reviewed.

58
00:05:17,125 --> 00:05:19,706
So that's something that's important to look at as well.

59
00:05:20,306 --> 00:05:20,586
Also,

60
00:05:21,526 --> 00:05:29,449
clarifying text that is confusing or disputed because of the particular structure of Medford's charter, which we'll be getting into.

61
00:05:31,850 --> 00:05:46,215
Some of it can be open to interpretation and we would want our charter to be as clear and understandable and accessible as possible so that any resident who's looking to see how our city government operates

62
00:05:46,855 --> 00:05:49,418
can go to the charter and they can understand it.

63
00:05:49,838 --> 00:05:54,083
Currently, that's challenging because of the nature of Medford's charter.

64
00:05:54,103 --> 00:05:59,769
And that also provides transparency on how our city government operates.

65
00:06:02,051 --> 00:06:07,577
