732
01:10:53,462 --> 01:10:56,445
Since we are an appointed committee, there is no deadline.

733
01:10:57,426 --> 01:11:01,170
In general, 18 months is considered

734
01:11:02,702 --> 01:11:12,768
A reasonable amount of time to do this if, if we had gone through the other avenue to charter review and had an elected commission, they would have a deadline and it would be 18 months.

735
01:11:13,449 --> 01:11:18,612
So we're currently at about six months, so we don't have a deadline but.

736
